r structures. These galaxies then consume their gas faster than\nthose in low-density regions through frequent interactions with other galaxies,\nending up being quiescent in the local universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jul 2019 22:14:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
