y\nof the above mechanisms by providing matching lower bounds. Our tight analysis\nfor the single-item deterministic case resolves an open gap from the work of\nAzar and Micali [ITCS'13].\n  As a by-product, we also show how one can directly use our upper bounds to\nimprove and extend previous results related to the parametric auctions of Azar\net al. [SODA'13].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jul 2019 14:56:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2019 10:16:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2022 16:35:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-29"}
