tion with a quantile\nlayer outperforms other architectures, e.g. previously proposed CNNs for the\nMRF reconstruction reducing the error in $T_1$ and $T_2$ by more than 80%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jul 2019 10:29:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 21 Jul 2019 13:06:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-23"}
